title: Wall Street Breakfast June 29: EU Endorses Push to End Internal Combustion Engine by 2035
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: EU endorses push to end internal combustion engine by 2035. PG&E asks for more time to apply for funds to keep nuclear plant open. NATO set to expand as Turkey backs membership for Sweden, Finland. FTC sues Walmart for facilitating fraud that 'fleeced customers' out of millions. Catch today’s WSB article here.
